; Regression test for issue #1082: balancing failure from precision
; infection.
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1082
;
; A high-precision USD amount in an unrelated transaction caused the
; commodity's balancing precision to widen, making a subsequent lot-cost
; transaction fail with "Transaction does not balance" even though it
; balanced perfectly at the commodity's natural 2-decimal precision.

